data.description: New lower price and a motivated seller!  You will fall in love with this beautiful house.  Pride of ownership shows throughout!  Updated kitchen with quartz counter tops and upgraded appliances. Refrigerator even makes craft ice.  Walk-in pantry is functional and stylish.  There is a built-in beer/wine cooler too.  Upgraded flooring and baseboards throughout the first floor.  Comfy carpet in the bedrooms and bonus room.  Master bedroom suite boasts his and hers closets; bathroom with dual sinks, a private water closet and storage galore.  Three additional bedrooms are good sized and there is also a bonus area that is currently used for watching movies.  Laundry room is on the second floor!  Updated half bath on the first floor is adorable.  Owners added convenient storage to the mudroom.  Large fenced back yard with a couple shade trees and tons of room to relax and play!  Enjoy the covered back patio for lounging & grilling.  This home even has new gutters.  The low annual fee includes use of the community amenities!  Includes; pool, gym, tennis court, basketball court, billiards room, splash pad and more!
